'''Lunis At Mengellat''', d amedyaz, d acennay i yellan yiwen seg inaẓuren imeẓẓwa ugar (plus populaires) n izwawen. Ilul ass n [[17 yennayer]] [[1950]], deg taddart n Iɣil Bbwamas ufella n [[Tamurt n leqbayel|tmurt n Leqbayel]] ar tama n Micli. Isɛa sdis warrac garasen yiwen d anazur n ccna : [[ǧeɛfer At Mengellat]].

